Revision history for Zef-Configuration

{{$NEXT}}

0.0.9  2022-02-24T17:44:36+01:00
    - Add support for "add-repository" to the CLI
    - Add support for "remove-repository" to the CLI
    - Add default for Z::C::Repository.module
    - Change default for Z::C::Repository.auto-update to 1
    - Some textual tweaks

0.0.8  2022-02-23T12:18:16+01:00
    - Fix version mismatch in zef-configure

0.0.7  2022-02-22T11:44:39+01:00
    - Fix problem with user dir if XDG_CONFIG_HOME is set
 
0.0.6  2022-02-19T12:26:00+01:00
    - Add dependency to "shorten-sub-commands"
    - Allow the CLI to use shortened sub commands
    - Upped dependency on JSON::Fast

0.0.5  2022-01-23T22:00:20+01:00
    - Fix basic testing, ugexe++ once again

0.0.4  2022-01-23T21:52:46+01:00
    - Add missing JSON::Fast dependency, ugexe++ for spotting

0.0.3  2022-01-23T21:19:28+01:00
    - Consider the config file found in Zef's resources as off-limits
    - Create config file in appropriate place (based on Zef's preferences)
      when making changes.
    - Added class method 'new-user-configuration'
    - Added class method 'is-configuration-writeable'
    - Fix default for "auto-update" in Zef::Configuration::Repository

0.0.2  2022-01-22T13:44:02+01:00
    - Add zef as a dependency so that we're guaranteed a default
      config that has the REA in it.

0.0.1  2022-01-18T12:26:10+01:00
    - Initial version
